      <title>Immigration arrests dip in July, and activists hope they're partly responsible</title>
      <author>Martin Kaste</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/08/16/nx-s1-5504144/immigration-arrests-dip-in-july-and-activists-hope-theyre-partly-responsible</link>
